  - The compilation’s aesthetic (funk, groove emphasis, single‑centric sequencing) increases the risk that synths/arrangements and bass/groove elements will dominate the midrange and low end, potentially masking piano/voice micro‑detail — a core thing I dislike.
Conclusion
